div.p: Veelderle niewe inventien van antcksche sepultueren diemen nou zeere ghebrukende is met noch zeer fraee grotissen en compertimenten zeer beqwame voer beeltsniders antcksniders schilders en alle constenaers ghedruckt b m Ieronmus . Cock . 1557 . C . FLORIS INVENT . LIBRO . SECUNDO . Cum gratia et privilegio .

Many new inventions of antique tombs, which is then very useful, with very charming grotesques and compartments, very fit for sculptors, antique-ornament sculptors, painters, and all artists. Printed by me, Hieronymus Cock. 1557. Invented by C[ornelis] Floris. Second book. With grace and privilege.
